abstract: Gifts recorded yesterday by The New York Times Neediest Cases Fund totaled $7,145.79 from 163 donors. This increased the donations to the 1967-68 appeal to $775,574.23 from 13,668 benefactors.
headline_main: Appeal for Neediest Gets 163 Donations; One Gift Is $3,1341; 163 IN A DAY GIVE TO THE NEEDIEST
